sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor You as PPC Manager
    participant Cloud as Google Cloud Console
    participant Ads as Google Ads (MCC)
    participant Term as Terminal<br/>(two included scripts)

    You->>Cloud: Create a project +<br/>enable the Ads API
    You->>Cloud: Consent screen —<br/>Internal or External
    Note over You,Cloud: Workspace org? Internal.<br/>Everyone else: External +<br/>PUBLISH to production.<br/>In Testing, tokens<br/>expire every 7 days.
    You->>Cloud: OAuth client —<br/>Desktop app type
    Cloud-->>You: client_secret.json
    You->>Ads: Admin → API Center
    Ads-->>You: Developer token
    You->>Term: generate_credentials.py
    You->>Cloud: Browser opens — sign in<br/>+ grant access (one time)
    Cloud-->>Term: Refresh token<br/>(long-lived login)
    You->>Term: Fill google-ads.yaml —<br/>five values, one file
    You->>Term: test_connection.py
    Term->>Ads: List the accounts<br/>under the MCC
    Ads-->>Term: Account list ✓
    Note over Term,Ads: Connection verified — and it<br/>stays working: the app was<br/>published, not left in Testing.
